---
const trialHref = "/trial/";
const walkthroughHref = "/schedule-a-walkthrough/";

---

<section class="section-hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-background" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/images/hero-office-background.svg" alt="" class="hero-background-image" />
  </div>
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1 class="hero-heading" aria-label="Your marketing should work as hard as you do.">
        <span class="hero-heading-line">Your marketing should work</span>
        <span class="hero-heading-line">as hard as you do.</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="hero-phone-chat" aria-label="A Markethink phone chat showing an AI operator, customer lead, and dedicated marketer coordinating the work.">
        <div class="phone-frame">
          <div class="phone-topbar">
            <span class="phone-camera" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>Markethink</strong>
              <span>Live marketing desk</span>
            </div>
            <span class="phone-status">Online</span>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-thread" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="chat-scene scene-lead">
              <div class="chat-bubble customer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">Customer lead</span>
                <p>Can someone send details tonight?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble ai-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">AI operator</span>
                <p>Reply ready with the offer, tone, and next step.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble marketer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">Dedicated marketer</span>
                <p>Approved. Send it and schedule the follow-up.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-scene scene-landing">
              <div class="chat-bubble customer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">You</span>
                <p>We need Friday’s landing page ready.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble ai-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">AI operator</span>
                <p>Hero, sections, CTA, and form copy are drafted.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble marketer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">Dedicated marketer</span>
                <p>Polished. Sending the page for approval.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-scene scene-social">
              <div class="chat-bubble customer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">You</span>
                <p>Turn this idea into social posts.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble ai-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">AI operator</span>
                <p>3 on-brand posts are ready with captions.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble marketer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">Dedicated marketer</span>
                <p>Ready to post now. Queue the next two.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-scene scene-campaign">
              <div class="chat-bubble customer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">You</span>
                <p>Start a campaign for the new service.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble ai-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">AI operator</span>
                <p>Campaign, landing, email, and leads are organized.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chat-bubble marketer-bubble">
                <span class="bubble-label">Dedicated marketer</span>
                <p>Good structure. Bring the first assets for review.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-description hero-heading-support">
        <p>An AI marketing operator does the work around the clock. A real marketer dedicated to your business reviews what ships. You approve from your phone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="button-group">
        <a href={walkthroughHref} class="button">Watch it work on your business →</a>
        <a href={trialHref} class="button is-secondary">Apply for a 30-Day Trial</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
    padding: clamp(7.4rem, 14vh, 8.7rem) 0 clamp(6.8rem, 13vh, 8.6rem);
    background: #0f1213;
  }

  .section-hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 46%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.24) 0%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.6) 48%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.88) 100%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.12) 0%, rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.44) 62%, #0f1213 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .section-hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.13), transparent 35rem);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -2;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-background-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    filter: saturate(0.96) contrast(1.04);
    transform: translateY(1.4rem) scale(1.015);
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: calc(100svh - clamp(14.2rem, 27vh, 17.3rem));
    padding-top: clamp(0.35rem, 1.8vh, 1rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 2vh, 1.25rem);
  }

  .hero-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(1.15rem, 2.2vh, 1.45rem);
    max-width: min(66rem, 92vw);
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-heading {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: min(58rem, 94vw);
    font-size: clamp(3.55rem, 5.6vw, 6.35rem);
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.058em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-heading-line {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-phone-chat {
    width: min(100%, 34rem);
    perspective: 1200px;
  }

  .phone-frame {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 0.82rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.2), rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.06) 42%, rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.12)),
      rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.48);
    box-shadow:
      0 28px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22),
      inset 0 -24px 54px rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(1.22);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(1.22);
  }

  .phone-frame::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -40% -18% auto auto;
    width: 18rem;
    height: 18rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.26), transparent 66%);
    filter: blur(4px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .phone-frame::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    background: linear-gradient(115deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24), transparent 24%, transparent 62%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08));
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .phone-topbar {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.72rem;
    padding: 0.28rem 0.38rem 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .phone-camera {
    width: 0.68rem;
    height: 0.68rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #69D254;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.32rem rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.14), 0 0 24px rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.5);
  }

  .phone-topbar strong,
  .phone-topbar span {
    display: block;
  }

  .phone-topbar strong {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .phone-topbar div span {
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.56);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .phone-status {
    padding: 0.36rem 0.62rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.14);
    color: #69D254;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .chat-thread {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    min-height: 12.9rem;
    padding: 0.15rem;
  }

  .chat-scene {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0.15rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.62rem;
    align-content: start;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(0.35rem) scale(0.992);
    animation: scene-cycle 24s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) infinite;
  }

  .scene-landing {
    animation-delay: 6s;
  }

  .scene-social {
    animation-delay: 12s;
  }

  .scene-campaign {
    animation-delay: 18s;
  }

  .chat-bubble {
    width: fit-content;
    max-width: 84%;
    padding: 0.72rem 0.86rem;
    border-radius: 1.12rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    background: rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.1);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .customer-bubble {
    justify-self: start;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 0.38rem;
  }

  .ai-bubble {
    justify-self: end;
    border-color: rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.28);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.2), rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.08));
    border-bottom-right-radius: 0.38rem;
  }

  .marketer-bubble {
    justify-self: start;
    background: rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.15);
    border-bottom-left-radius: 0.38rem;
  }

  .bubble-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.24rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .chat-bubble p {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 1vw, 0.96rem);
    font-weight: 650;
    line-height: 1.32;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  @keyframes scene-cycle {
    0%, 4% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(0.35rem) scale(0.992);
    }

    9%, 22% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }

    25%, 100% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-0.28rem) scale(0.996);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .chat-scene {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: none;
    }

    .chat-scene:first-child {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .hero-description {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    max-width: 46rem;
  }

  .hero-heading-support {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.1em;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.12vw, 1.16rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.48;
    letter-spacing: -0.018em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-heading-support p {
    margin: 0;
  }


  .button-group {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: clamp(0.35rem, 1vh, 0.75rem);
  }

  .button-group .button {
    min-height: 3.45rem;
    padding-inline: 1.55rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 0.95vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .button-group .button.is-secondary {
    color: #ffffff;
    border-color: rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.82);
    background: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.18);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }


  @media (max-width: 1180px) {
    .hero-text {
      max-width: min(64rem, 94vw);
    }

    .hero-heading {
      max-width: min(62rem, 94vw);
      font-size: clamp(3.05rem, 6vw, 5.75rem);
    }

    .section-hero::before {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 42%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.34) 0%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.7) 52%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.9) 100%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.14) 0%, rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.24) 58%, #0f1213 100%);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .section-hero {
      min-height: 100svh;
      padding: 7.2rem 0 5.7rem;
    }

    .hero-content {
      min-height: calc(100svh - 12.9rem);
    }

    .hero-background-image {
      object-position: 62% top;
      transform: translateY(1rem) scale(1.02);
    }

    .section-hero::before {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.78) 0%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.7) 46%, #0f1213 100%),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.78) 0%, rgba(4, 6, 6, 0.3) 100%);
    }

    .hero-text {
      max-width: 100%;
      gap: 1.05rem;
    }

    .hero-heading {
      max-width: 100%;
      font-size: clamp(2.45rem, 10vw, 3.55rem);
    }

    .hero-phone-chat {
      width: min(100%, 31rem);
    }

    .phone-frame {
      border-radius: 1.55rem;
      padding: 0.72rem;
    }

    .chat-bubble {
      max-width: 88%;
    }

    .hero-description {
      max-width: 34rem;
    }

    .hero-heading-support {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 4.2vw, 1.25rem);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .section-hero {
      padding-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .hero-content {
      min-height: calc(100svh - 12.2rem);
    }

    .hero-heading {
      font-size: clamp(2.08rem, 10.6vw, 2.9rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    }

    .hero-phone-chat {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .phone-topbar {
      gap: 0.56rem;
    }

    .phone-status {
      display: none;
    }

    .chat-bubble p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .hero-heading-support {
      font-size: clamp(0.98rem, 4.6vw, 1.16rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.018em;
    }

    .button-group,
    .button-group .button {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .button-group .button {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
